    //   aligned. For odd n_global at small C_out (3,4,5,7) this is <8-byte
    //   aligned → unaligned cp.async yields garbage / replicated data for
    //   odd n-rows. Observed as silent corruption at the last C_in column
    //   (only the c_in=63 slot failed; odd c_in positions silently dropped
    //   their weight contribution and spilled into adjacent even c_in).
    //   See notes/2026_04_17_codegen_drift_audit.md for the analogue on the
