  // sub-16B weight base (DeepSpeed ZeRO contiguous-view weights) faults
  // "misaligned address". Guard on (base | stride*sizeof); scalar fallback
  // when misaligned. Stride: N (fwd, N-contig) / K_dim (transposed).
